						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">I wonder to what extent the BRR data itself could be compressed.</div><br />Trust me, very poorly.<br />I have tested this. Even very advanced compressions such as BZIP2 will not compress anything when compressing BRR data.<br />The only thing you could possibly do is separate the BRR header data from the other data and compress the header efficiently, but even then you'll never compress more than 1/9 of the whole data which is very poor.</div>

