						<div class="postbody">Okay, here is a simple algorithm to start with.  Obviously it's not going to be the final algorithm, but it's a starting place.<br /><br />mmrrrrrr<br /><br />m: mode<br />00: solid black tile<br />01: solid white tile<br />10: 1 bpp tile<br />11: 2 bpp tile<br /><br />r: run legnth (1-64)<br /><br />BTW, aren't tiles in hi-res mode always 16 pixels across?</div>

